Today, we are pleased to announce the launch of Nation Puzzles on Nation.Africa. This new feature will contain daily crosswords, sudoku, word searches and so much more that is designed to give our audiences and registered members a fresh way to challenge themselves and simulate their minds.
Nation Puzzles gives us a unique opportunity to leverage on a classic product that has featured in our dailies for over 5 decades, to reach and attract new audiences by repurposing it for a digital platform that is easily accessible and interactive on mobile.



