This milestone comes off the back of achieving a subscriber base of 160,000 registered users on Nation.Africa since launch in August this year. We believe that delivering these digital interactive puzzles will propel us to a new frontier of growth while fostering deeper connections with our customers.  





We will give them a new way to challenge their minds and sharpen their mental acuity, while also providing an avenue for a well-deserved break from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.
